data.body:
For language c family, when a line continued in the next line, 4 spaces is needed instead of 2 space.
One way to support this is that, language-model add two regex config: doubleIncreaseIndentPattern, doubleDecreaseNextIndentPattern
Expected:

``` c++
void main () {
  function(
      a,
      b);
  }
}
```

Version 1.7.3 gives:

``` c++
void main () {
  function(
    a,
    b);
  }
}
```
